Usage: chpl [flags|source files]

Compilation Traces:
-------------------
      --print-passes      set on   false     Print compiler passes
      --print-commands    set on   false     Print system commands

Code Size Statistics:
---------------------
      --print-code-size   set on   false     Print Tokens
      --count-tokens      set on   false     Count tokens

Optimization Control:
---------------------
      --no-bounds-checks  set on   false     Disable bounds checking
      --no-inline         set on   false     Do not inline functions
      --unoptimized       set on   false     Generate naive code (many temps)

Code Generation:
----------------
      --cg-cpp-lines      set on   false     Generate #line annotations
      --cg-chpl-lineno    set on   false     Generate line numbers for errors
      --savec             path     (null)    Save generated C code
  -p, --parallel          toggle   true      toggle threaded code generation

Linker Control:
---------------
  -o, --output            path     a.out     Name output executable
  -L, --lib-search-path   path     (null)    C library search path
  -l, --lib-linkage       path     (null)    C library linkage
      --ccflags           string   -g        Back-end C compiler flags

Miscellaneous Flags:
--------------------
      --gdb               set on   false     Run compiler in gdb
      --instantiate-max   int      256       Limit number of instantiations
      --chplhome          path     .         Chapel location
      --devel             set on   true      Compile as developer

Compiler Information:
---------------------
      --version                              Show Version
      --copyright                            Show Copyright
      --license                              Show License
  -h, --help                                 Help (show this list)


Developer Flags
===============

Debug Output:
-------------
  -t, --html              toggle   false     Dump IR in HTML
      --print-statistics  string   (null)    Print AST statistics
  -D, --parser-debug      incr     0         Parser debug level
      --report-inlining   set on   false     Print inlined functions
  -d, --log               string   (null)    Debug logging flags
      --log-dir           path     ./log     Log directory

Optimization Control:
---------------------
      --formal-temps      set on   false     Insert temps for formals
      --no-scalar-replacement toggle   true      **INVERTED** Do not scalar replace marked records (e.g. tuples)

Overriding defaults:
--------------------
      --nostdincs         toggle   false     No standard modules
      --no-codegen        set on   false     Suppress code generation
      --ignore-errors     set on   false     Attempt to ignore errors
      --scalar-promotion  toggle   true      Enable scalar promotion
